items.Subject: Re: Summer brochure 2021
items.RawHtmlBody:
Hi Terry,
Nice to hear from you, I hope you're well.
Sure, our summer brochure is already out 😎! I've attached it together with our winter brochure ⛄.

I've heard you're a massive fan of rubber ducks, so I wanted to share with you this picture I took this summer. Amazing, eh?


Any questions (about the brochures, not the ducks 😜), I'd be happy to help.

Speak soon,  
Antoine Lefeuvre
Co-founder & Product Manager at MailClark
antoine@mailclark.ai
Twitter LinkedIn
Sent with MailClark


On Tue, 1 Sep 2020 at 09:43, Terry Estill <test@clubble.me> wrote:

Hi there, I hope things with you are good.

I was wondering whether your brochure for the summer next year was already available. I'm willing to start planning asap.

Best,

--
Terry Estill—Cofounder & CEO
The Wheat Assembly - Le Club Blé
test@clubble.me
www.clubble.me
